### =========================
### POST /reservations(予約登録)
### =========================

### 1. 正常
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "room_id": 2,
  "check_in": "2026-05-29",
  "check_out": "2026-05-30",
  "guest_count": 2
}

### 2. 重複予約（409）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "room_id": 21,
  "check_in": "2026-05-10",
  "check_out": "2026-05-12",
  "guest_count": 1
}

### 3. 定員超過（400）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "room_id": 24,
  "check_in": "2026-05-20",
  "check_out": "2026-05-22",
  "guest_count": 3
}

### =========================
### PATCH /reservations/[reservationId]/cancel(予約キャンセル)
### =========================
### 4. 予約キャンセル
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/58/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. すでにキャンセル済み（400）
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/reservations/58/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}